<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/9267> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #9267" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "The list of senators in a dated inscription of this year (SIG(3) 747) provides good evidence for the names of a group of ex-magistrates, although it is not wholly conclusive because of the additions to the Senate by the reforms of Sulla." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/8188> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #8188" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Senator. In MRR 2.475, refer also to Plin. NH 8.167, a notice taken from Varro.\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6684> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6684" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/3> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Senator, probably quaestorius, and fellow-tribesman of Varro (RR 3.2. 1), and a friend and correspondent of Cicero." .
